{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1957,"text":"Let me tell you a story"},{"time":3518,"text":"about a little girl named Naghma."},{"time":6724,"text":"Naghma lived in a refugee camp"},{"time":8546,"text":"with her parents and her eight brothers and sisters."},{"time":11425,"text":"Every morning, her father would wake up"},{"time":13361,"text":"in the hopes he'd be picked for construction work,"},{"time":15801,"text":"and on a good month he would earn 50 dollars."},{"time":19367,"text":"The winter was very harsh,"},{"time":20755,"text":"and unfortunately, Naghma's brother died"},{"time":23439,"text":"and her mother became very ill."},{"time":25359,"text":"In desperation, her father went to a neighbor"},{"time":27939,"text":"to borrow 2,500 dollars."},{"time":30336,"text":"After several months of waiting,"},{"time":32250,"text":"the neighbor became very impatient,"},{"time":33767,"text":"and he demanded that he be paid back."},{"time":36485,"text":"Unfortunately, Naghma's\nfather didn't have the money,"},{"time":38929,"text":"and so the two men agreed to a jirga."},{"time":41764,"text":"So simply put, a jirga is a form of mediation"},{"time":44294,"text":"that's used in Afghanistan's \ninformal justice system."},{"time":47534,"text":"It's usually presided over by religious leaders"},{"time":50988,"text":"and village elders,"},{"time":52686,"text":"and jirgas are often used in\nrural countries like Afghanistan,"},{"time":55886,"text":"where there's deep-seated resentment"},{"time":57737,"text":"against the formal system."},{"time":59999,"text":"At the jirga, the men sat together"},{"time":62337,"text":"and they decided that the \nbest way to satisfy the debt"},{"time":65251,"text":"would be if Naghma married\nthe neighbor's 21-year-old son."},{"time":69840,"text":"She was six."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72500,"text":"Now, stories like Naghma's unfortunately"},{"time":74565,"text":"are all too common,"},{"time":76253,"text":"and from the comforts of our home,"},{"time":77748,"text":"we may look at these stories as another"},{"time":79503,"text":"crushing blow to women's rights."},{"time":81763,"text":"And if you watched Afghanistan on the news,"},{"time":84294,"text":"you may have this view that it's a failed state."},{"time":87993,"text":"However, Afghanistan does have a legal system,"},{"time":91809,"text":"and while jirgas are built on\nlong-standing tribal customs,"},{"time":95671,"text":"even in jirgas, laws are supposed to be followed,"},{"time":99034,"text":"and it goes without saying"},{"time":100962,"text":"that giving a child to satisfy a debt"},{"time":103583,"text":"is not only grossly immoral, it's illegal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107649,"text":"In 2008, I went to Afghanistan"},{"time":110176,"text":"for a justice funded program,"},{"time":112496,"text":"and I went there originally \non this nine-month program"},{"time":115203,"text":"to train Afghan lawyers."},{"time":117115,"text":"In that nine months, I went around the country"},{"time":119376,"text":"and I talked to hundreds of\npeople that were locked up,"},{"time":122312,"text":"and I talked to many businesses"},{"time":123910,"text":"that were also operating in Afghanistan."},{"time":126440,"text":"And within these conversations,"},{"time":127784,"text":"I started hearing the connections"},{"time":129655,"text":"between the businesses and the people,"},{"time":131645,"text":"and how laws that were meant to protect them"},{"time":133715,"text":"were being underused,"},{"time":135416,"text":"while gross and illegal punitive\nmeasures were overused."},{"time":139474,"text":"And so this put me on a quest for justness,"},{"time":142298,"text":"and what justness means to me"},{"time":145020,"text":"is using laws for their intended purpose,"},{"time":148715,"text":"which is to protect."},{"time":151040,"text":"The role of laws is to protect."},{"time":154543,"text":"So as a result, I decided to \nopen up a private practice,"},{"time":158258,"text":"and I became the first foreigner to litigate"},{"time":160599,"text":"in Afghan courts."},{"time":162815,"text":"Throughout this time, I also studied many laws,"},{"time":165672,"text":"I talked to many people,"},{"time":167202,"text":"I read up on many cases,"},{"time":168373,"text":"and I found that the lack of justness"},{"time":170763,"text":"is not just a problem in Afghanistan,"},{"time":172749,"text":"but it's a global problem."},{"time":175070,"text":"And while I originally shied away from"},{"time":176821,"text":"representing human rights cases"},{"time":178938,"text":"because I was really concerned about how it would"},{"time":181117,"text":"affect me both professionally and personally,"},{"time":183760,"text":"I decided that the need for justness was so great"},{"time":186513,"text":"that I couldn't continue to ignore it."},{"time":188384,"text":"And so I started representing people like Naghma"},{"time":190701,"text":"pro bono also."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193157,"text":"Now, since I've been in Afghanistan"},{"time":194863,"text":"and since I've been an attorney for over 10 years,"},{"time":197326,"text":"I've represented from CEOs \nof Fortune 500 companies"},{"time":201040,"text":"to ambassadors to little girls like Naghma,"},{"time":203368,"text":"and with much success."},{"time":204918,"text":"And the reason for my success is very simple:"},{"time":207833,"text":"I work the system from the inside out"},{"time":209843,"text":"and use the laws in the ways"},{"time":211262,"text":"that they're intended to be used."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213998,"text":"I find that"},{"time":216120,"text":"achieving justness in places like Afghanistan"},{"time":219536,"text":"is difficult, and there's three reasons."},{"time":221684,"text":"The first reason is that simply put,"},{"time":224240,"text":"people are very uneducated as\nto what their legal rights were,"},{"time":227339,"text":"and I find that this is a global problem."},{"time":229930,"text":"The second issue"},{"time":231144,"text":"is that even with laws on the books,"},{"time":234583,"text":"it's often superseded or ignored"},{"time":236848,"text":"by tribal customs, like in the first jirga"},{"time":239170,"text":"that sold Naghma off."},{"time":240702,"text":"And the third problem with achieving justness"},{"time":243404,"text":"is that even with good, existing laws on the books,"},{"time":246216,"text":"there aren't people or lawyers \nthat are willing to fight"},{"time":248862,"text":"for those laws."},{"time":250558,"text":"And that's what I do: I use existing laws,"},{"time":253432,"text":"often unused laws,"},{"time":255231,"text":"and I work those to the benefits of my clients."},{"time":258865,"text":"We all need to create a global culture"},{"time":261413,"text":"of human rights"},{"time":263241,"text":"and be investors in a global \nhuman rights economy,"},{"time":265990,"text":"and by working in this mindset,"},{"time":267757,"text":"we can significantly improve justice globally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270474,"text":"Now let's get back to Naghma."},{"time":272866,"text":"Several people heard about this story,"},{"time":275265,"text":"and so they contacted me because they wanted"},{"time":276790,"text":"to pay the $2,500 debt."},{"time":279355,"text":"And it's not just that simple;"},{"time":281216,"text":"you can't just throw money at this problem"},{"time":282998,"text":"and think that it's going to disappear."},{"time":284151,"text":"That's not how it works in Afghanistan."},{"time":286632,"text":"So I told them I'd get involved,"},{"time":290030,"text":"but in order to get involved, \nwhat needed to happen"},{"time":292318,"text":"is a second jirga needed to be called,"},{"time":295141,"text":"a jirga of appeals."},{"time":297250,"text":"And so in order for that to happen,"},{"time":299501,"text":"we needed to get the village elders together,"},{"time":302206,"text":"we needed to get the tribal leaders together,"},{"time":304467,"text":"the religious leaders."},{"time":306056,"text":"Naghma's father needed to agree,"},{"time":307630,"text":"the neighbor needed to agree,"},{"time":308881,"text":"and also his son needed to agree."},{"time":311085,"text":"And I thought, if I'm going to \nget involved in this thing,"},{"time":315110,"text":"then they also need to agree \nthat I preside over it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318765,"text":"So, after hours of talking"},{"time":321735,"text":"and tracking them down,"},{"time":322943,"text":"and about 30 cups of tea,"},{"time":325806,"text":"they finally agreed that we could sit down"},{"time":327718,"text":"for a second jirga, and we did."},{"time":331050,"text":"And what was different about the second jirga"},{"time":333134,"text":"is this time, we put the law at the center of it,"},{"time":335709,"text":"and it was very important for me"},{"time":337053,"text":"that they all understood that Naghma"},{"time":338811,"text":"had a right to be protected."},{"time":341150,"text":"And at the end of this jirga,"},{"time":342696,"text":"it was ordered by the judge"},{"time":344989,"text":"that the first decision was erased,"},{"time":348825,"text":"and that the $2,500 debt was satisfied,"},{"time":352257,"text":"and we all signed a written order"},{"time":354090,"text":"where all the men acknowledged"},{"time":355481,"text":"that what they did was illegal,"},{"time":357601,"text":"and if they did it again, that \nthey would go to prison."},{"time":362399,"text":"Most —"},{"time":364168,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":365636,"text":"Thanks."},{"time":367483,"text":"And most importantly,"},{"time":369299,"text":"the engagement was terminated"},{"time":370800,"text":"and Naghma was free."},{"time":372809,"text":"Protecting Naghma and her right to be free"},{"time":375666,"text":"protects us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378300,"text":"Now, with my job, there's above-average"},{"time":381762,"text":"amount of risks that are involved."},{"time":384505,"text":"I've been temporarily detained."},{"time":387212,"text":"I've been accused of running a brothel,"},{"time":389805,"text":"accused of being a spy."},{"time":392110,"text":"I've had a grenade thrown at my office."},{"time":394238,"text":"It didn't go off, though."},{"time":396937,"text":"But I find that with my job,"},{"time":398537,"text":"that the rewards far outweigh the risks,"},{"time":401503,"text":"and as many risks as I take,"},{"time":403877,"text":"my clients take far greater risks,"},{"time":405846,"text":"because they have a lot more to lose"},{"time":407349,"text":"if their cases go unheard,"},{"time":408839,"text":"or worse, if they're penalized\nfor having me as their lawyer."},{"time":411962,"text":"With every case that I take,"},{"time":413736,"text":"I realize that as much as\nI'm standing behind my clients,"},{"time":416656,"text":"that they're also standing behind me,"},{"time":418669,"text":"and that's what keeps me going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422462,"text":"Law as a point of leverage"},{"time":424359,"text":"is crucial in protecting all of us."},{"time":426881,"text":"Journalists are very vital in making sure"},{"time":429517,"text":"that that information is given to the public."},{"time":432791,"text":"Too often, we receive information from journalists"},{"time":435277,"text":"but we forget how that information was given."},{"time":438921,"text":"This picture is a picture of the"},{"time":441507,"text":"British press corps in Afghanistan."},{"time":443500,"text":"It was taken a couple of years\nago by my friend David Gill."},{"time":446649,"text":"According to the Committee to Protect Journalists,"},{"time":448517,"text":"since 2010, there have been \nthousands of journalists"},{"time":451363,"text":"who have been threatened, injured,"},{"time":453241,"text":"killed, detained."},{"time":455873,"text":"Too often, when we get this information,"},{"time":458112,"text":"we forget who it affects"},{"time":459336,"text":"or how that information is given to us."},{"time":462634,"text":"What many journalists do, \nboth foreign and domestic,"},{"time":465244,"text":"is very remarkable, especially\nin places like Afghanistan,"},{"time":469315,"text":"and it's important that we never forget that,"},{"time":470887,"text":"because what they're protecting"},{"time":472243,"text":"is not only our right to receive that information"},{"time":474525,"text":"but also the freedom of the press, which is vital"},{"time":476582,"text":"to a democratic society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479458,"text":"Matt Rosenberg is a journalist in Afghanistan."},{"time":483343,"text":"He works for The New York Times,"},{"time":485233,"text":"and unfortunately, a few months ago"},{"time":486850,"text":"he wrote an article that displeased"},{"time":488990,"text":"people in the government."},{"time":490296,"text":"As a result, he was temporarily detained"},{"time":493546,"text":"and he was illegally exiled out of the country."},{"time":497859,"text":"I represent Matt,"},{"time":499911,"text":"and after dealing with the government,"},{"time":502039,"text":"I was able to get legal acknowledgment"},{"time":503719,"text":"that in fact he was illegally exiled,"},{"time":506780,"text":"and that freedom of the\npress does exist in Afghanistan,"},{"time":509840,"text":"and there's consequences if that's not followed."},{"time":512372,"text":"And I'm happy to say that"},{"time":514118,"text":"as of a few days ago,"},{"time":516206,"text":"the Afghan government"},{"time":517532,"text":"formally invited him back into the country"},{"time":519744,"text":"and they reversed their exile order of him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523377,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":528049,"text":"If you censor one journalist, \nthen it intimidates others,"},{"time":531252,"text":"and soon nations are silenced."},{"time":533224,"text":"It's important that we protect our journalists"},{"time":535942,"text":"and freedom of the press,"},{"time":537719,"text":"because that makes governments\nmore accountable to us"},{"time":539778,"text":"and more transparent."},{"time":541763,"text":"Protecting journalists and our right"},{"time":543670,"text":"to receive information protects us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547844,"text":"Our world is changing. We live\nin a different world now,"},{"time":550860,"text":"and what were once individual problems"},{"time":553243,"text":"are really now global problems for all of us."},{"time":556061,"text":"Two weeks ago, Afghanistan had its first"},{"time":559700,"text":"democratic transfer of power"},{"time":561691,"text":"and elected president Ashraf Ghani, which is huge,"},{"time":564943,"text":"and I'm very optimistic about him,"},{"time":567440,"text":"and I'm hopeful that he'll give Afghanistan"},{"time":569419,"text":"the changes that it needs,"},{"time":570690,"text":"especially within the legal sector."},{"time":573187,"text":"We live in a different world."},{"time":575090,"text":"We live in a world where my \neight-year-old daughter"},{"time":577439,"text":"only knows a black president."},{"time":580153,"text":"There's a great possibility that our next president"},{"time":582861,"text":"will be a woman,"},{"time":584197,"text":"and as she gets older, she may question,"},{"time":587100,"text":"can a white guy be president?"},{"time":588845,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":590619,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":593730,"text":"Our world is changing, and \nwe need to change with it,"},{"time":596910,"text":"and what were once individual problems"},{"time":598542,"text":"are problems for all of us."},{"time":601390,"text":"According to UNICEF,"},{"time":603468,"text":"there are currently over 280 million"},{"time":609509,"text":"boys and girls who are married"},{"time":611394,"text":"under the age of 15."},{"time":613176,"text":"Two hundred and eighty million."},{"time":615219,"text":"Child marriages prolong the vicious cycle"},{"time":617761,"text":"of poverty, poor health, lack of education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622181,"text":"At the age of 12, Sahar was married."},{"time":626868,"text":"She was forced into this marriage"},{"time":628717,"text":"and sold by her brother."},{"time":630417,"text":"When she went to her in-laws' house,"},{"time":632485,"text":"they forced her into prostitution."},{"time":635173,"text":"Because she refused, she was tortured."},{"time":638986,"text":"She was severely beaten with metal rods."},{"time":643011,"text":"They burned her body."},{"time":645803,"text":"They tied her up in a basement and starved her."},{"time":649293,"text":"They used pliers to take out her fingernails."},{"time":653503,"text":"At one point,"},{"time":655332,"text":"she managed to escape from this torture chamber"},{"time":658537,"text":"to a neighbor's house,"},{"time":660910,"text":"and when she went there, instead of protecting her,"},{"time":664206,"text":"they dragged her back"},{"time":666221,"text":"to her husband's house,"},{"time":667857,"text":"and she was tortured even worse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673864,"text":"When I met first Sahar, thankfully,"},{"time":676975,"text":"Women for Afghan Women"},{"time":678206,"text":"gave her a safe haven to go to."},{"time":681534,"text":"As a lawyer, I try to be very strong"},{"time":684720,"text":"for all my clients,"},{"time":686379,"text":"because that's very important to me,"},{"time":690193,"text":"but seeing her,"},{"time":693122,"text":"how broken and very weak as she was,"},{"time":697024,"text":"was very difficult."},{"time":700321,"text":"It took weeks for us to really get to"},{"time":703808,"text":"what happened to her"},{"time":707164,"text":"when she was in that house,"},{"time":709120,"text":"but finally she started opening up to me,"},{"time":711760,"text":"and when she opened up,"},{"time":714080,"text":"what I heard was"},{"time":715552,"text":"she didn't know what her rights were,"},{"time":718152,"text":"but she did know she had \na certain level of protection"},{"time":720355,"text":"by her government that failed her,"},{"time":722982,"text":"and so we were able to talk about"},{"time":724584,"text":"what her legal options were."}]},{"cues":[{"time":727126,"text":"And so we decided to take this case"},{"time":729134,"text":"to the Supreme Court."},{"time":730890,"text":"Now, this is extremely significant,"},{"time":732760,"text":"because this is the first time"},{"time":734673,"text":"that a victim of domestic violence in Afghanistan"},{"time":737509,"text":"was being represented by a lawyer,"},{"time":740302,"text":"a law that's been on the \nbooks for years and years,"},{"time":743037,"text":"but until Sahar, had never been used."},{"time":746443,"text":"In addition to this, we also decided"},{"time":748655,"text":"to sue for civil damages,"},{"time":750378,"text":"again using a law that's never been used,"},{"time":753325,"text":"but we used it for her case."},{"time":756353,"text":"So there we were at the Supreme Court"},{"time":758615,"text":"arguing in front of 12 Afghan justices,"},{"time":761857,"text":"me as an American female lawyer,"},{"time":764493,"text":"and Sahar, a young woman"},{"time":767980,"text":"who when I met her couldn't \nspeak above a whisper."},{"time":773163,"text":"She stood up,"},{"time":774834,"text":"she found her voice,"},{"time":777120,"text":"and my girl told them that she wanted justice,"},{"time":779917,"text":"and she got it."},{"time":782556,"text":"At the end of it all, the court unanimously agreed"},{"time":785385,"text":"that her in-laws should be\narrested for what they did to her,"},{"time":789568,"text":"her fucking brother should also be arrested"},{"time":792177,"text":"for selling her —"},{"time":794123,"text":"(Applause) —"},{"time":798543,"text":"and they agreed that she did have a right"},{"time":800546,"text":"to civil compensation."},{"time":802964,"text":"What Sahar has shown us is that we can attack"},{"time":805743,"text":"existing bad practices by using the laws"},{"time":808521,"text":"in the ways that they're intended to be used,"},{"time":811459,"text":"and by protecting Sahar,"},{"time":813940,"text":"we are protecting ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":817520,"text":"After having worked in Afghanistan"},{"time":819152,"text":"for over six years now,"},{"time":821150,"text":"a lot of my family and friends think"},{"time":823201,"text":"that what I do looks like this."},{"time":825993,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":828499,"text":"But in all actuality, what I do looks like this."},{"time":833137,"text":"Now, we can all do something."},{"time":835010,"text":"I'm not saying we should all buy a\nplane ticket and go to Afghanistan,"},{"time":837790,"text":"but we can all be contributors"},{"time":840812,"text":"to a global human rights economy."},{"time":842871,"text":"We can create a culture of transparency"},{"time":845139,"text":"and accountability to the laws,"},{"time":846463,"text":"and make governments more accountable to us,"},{"time":848874,"text":"as we are to them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":851897,"text":"A few months ago, a South African lawyer"},{"time":853889,"text":"visited me in my office"},{"time":855644,"text":"and he said, \"I wanted to meet you."},{"time":857569,"text":"I wanted to see what a crazy person looked like.\""},{"time":861563,"text":"The laws are ours,"},{"time":863542,"text":"and no matter what your ethnicity,"},{"time":865575,"text":"nationality, gender, race,"},{"time":868466,"text":"they belong to us,"},{"time":870585,"text":"and fighting for justice is not an act of insanity."},{"time":875374,"text":"Businesses also need to get with the program."},{"time":877615,"text":"A corporate investment in human rights"},{"time":879336,"text":"is a capital gain on your businesses,"},{"time":881214,"text":"and whether you're a business, an NGO,"},{"time":883340,"text":"or a private citizen, rule \nof law benefits all of us."},{"time":887435,"text":"And by working together with a concerted mindset,"},{"time":889750,"text":"through the people, public and private sector,"},{"time":893206,"text":"we can create a global human rights economy"},{"time":895503,"text":"and all become global investors in human rights."},{"time":899036,"text":"And by doing this,"},{"time":900820,"text":"we can achieve justness together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":903480,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":905573,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}